                                        <P>
                                            You have recently started a new job, a new study course or some other new
                                            activity and you are writing to your friends <B>in French</B> via an online
                                            forum about your daily, weekly, weekend and annual routines (e.g. holidays and
                                            seasonal activities). The information you give can be true or fictional. Your
                                            text should be <B>between 120 and 200 words </B>(advisory length).
                                        </P>
                                        <P>You should include the following information:</P>
                                        <UL class="oucontent-bulleted">
                                            <LI>your daily personal routines</LI>
                                            <LI>
                                                your daily work/study/activity routines (if work, it can be anything
                                                including paid, unpaid or voluntary)
                                            </LI>
                                            <LI>your weekend and holiday routines</LI>
                                            <LI>
                                                what you intend to do the following weekend or on a forthcoming
                                                holiday.
                                            </LI>
                                        </UL>
                                        <P>
                                            You should use the following language structures and vocabulary you have
                                            learned in <I><SPAN lang="fr" lang="fr" xml:lang="fr">Unité</SPAN></I> 5:
                                        </P>
                                        <UL class="oucontent-bulleted">
                                            <LI>pronominal verbs </LI>
                                            <LI>
                                                expressions of time (use figures or write in full, but be
                                                consistent&nbsp;: <I>8&nbsp;h&nbsp;30</I> or <SPAN lang="fr" lang="fr"
                                                                                                   xml:lang="fr"><I> huit heures et demie</I></SPAN>)
                                            </LI>
                                            <LI>days of the week</LI>
                                            <LI>months and seasons </LI>
                                            <LI>job titles and occupations (if applicable)</LI>
                                            <LI>work or study patterns (if applicable)</LI>
                                            <LI>expressing intention.</LI>
                                        </UL>
                                        <P>
                                            <B>
                                                When you have finished, count the number of words and write this number at
                                                the end of your assignment.
                                            </B>
                                        </P>
                                        <P>
